- ‚úÖ **Use native HTML elements**: Better accessibility built-in
- ‚úÖ **Proper heading hierarchy**: h1 ‚Üí h2 ‚Üí h3 (don't skip)
- ‚úÖ **Semantic landmarks**: `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<footer>`
