#### Buttons vs Links
- ‚úÖ **`<button>` for actions**: Submit, open, toggle
- ‚úÖ **`<a>` for navigation**: Going to another page
- ‚úÖ **Never use `<div>` or `<span>` for clickable elements**

```html
