```

### ARIA (Accessible Rich Internet Applications)

#### ARIA Roles
- ‚úÖ **Use native HTML first**: ARIA should supplement, not replace
- ‚úÖ **Role when needed**: `role="button"`, `role="dialog"`, etc.
- ‚úÖ **Landmark roles**: For better navigation
- ‚úÖ **Don't override native semantics**

```html
<!-- ‚úÖ Good: ARIA roles for custom components -->
<div 
  role="dialog" 
  aria-labelledby="modal-title"
  aria-describedby="modal-desc"
  aria-modal="true">
  
  <h2 id="modal-title">Confirm Action</h2>
  <p id="modal-desc">Are you sure you want to delete this item?</p>
  
  <button type="button">Cancel</button>
  <button type="button">Delete</button>
</div>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: ARIA for tabs -->
<div role="tablist" aria-label="Content sections">
  <button 
    role="tab" 
    aria-selected="true"
    aria-controls="panel-1"
    id="tab-1">
    Tab 1
  </button>
  <button 
    role="tab" 
    aria-selected="false"
    aria-controls="panel-2"
    id="tab-2">
    Tab 2
  </button>
</div>

<div id="panel-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-1">
  Content for tab 1
</div>

<div id="panel-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-2" hidden>
  Content for tab 2
</div>
```

#### ARIA Labels and Descriptions
- ‚úÖ **`aria-label`**: Provides label when none visible
- ‚úÖ **`aria-labelledby`**: References visible label
- ‚úÖ **`aria-describedby`**: Additional description
- ‚úÖ **`aria-hidden`**: Hides decorative elements from screen readers

```html
<!-- ‚úÖ Good: ARIA labels for icons/buttons -->
<button aria-label="Close dialog">
  <svg aria-hidden="true">
    <use href="#icon-close"></use>
  </svg>
</button>

<button aria-label="Search">
  üîç
</button>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: aria-labelledby for form groups -->
<fieldset>
  <legend id="shipping-legend">Shipping Address</legend>
  
  <div role="group" aria-labelledby="shipping-legend">
    <label for="street">Street</label>
    <input type="text" id="street" name="street">
    
    <label for="city">City</label>
    <input type="text" id="city" name="city">
  </div>
</fieldset>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: aria-describedby for hints -->
<label for="password">Password</label>
<input 
  type="password" 
  id="password" 
  aria-describedby="password-hint">
<span id="password-hint">Must be at least 8 characters</span>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: aria-hidden for decorative elements -->
