```

#### ARIA States and Properties
- ‚úÖ **`aria-expanded`**: For collapsible content
- ‚úÖ **`aria-checked`**: For custom checkboxes
- ‚úÖ **`aria-disabled`**: For disabled elements
- ‚úÖ **`aria-invalid`**: For form validation
- ‚úÖ **`aria-live`**: For dynamic content updates

```html
<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Accordion with ARIA -->
<div class="accordion">
  <button 
    aria-expanded="false"
    aria-controls="section-1"
    id="accordion-1">
    Section 1
  </button>
  
  <div id="section-1" role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-1" hidden>
    <p>Content for section 1</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Custom checkbox -->
<div 
  role="checkbox" 
  aria-checked="false"
  tabindex="0"
  aria-labelledby="checkbox-label">
  <span id="checkbox-label">I agree to terms</span>
</div>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Form validation -->
<label for="email">Email</label>
<input 
  type="email" 
  id="email"
  aria-invalid="true"
  aria-describedby="email-error">
<span id="email-error" role="alert">
  Please enter a valid email address
</span>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Live region for notifications -->
<div 
  role="status" 
  aria-live="polite" 
  aria-atomic="true"
  class="notification">
  <!-- Dynamically inserted messages appear here -->
</div>

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Alert for important messages -->
<div role="alert" aria-live="assertive">
  Your session will expire in 5 minutes
</div>
```

### Keyboard Navigation

#### Focus Management
- ‚úÖ **All interactive elements focusable**: Tab index 0 or native
- ‚úÖ **Visible focus indicators**: Clear outline or ring
- ‚úÖ **Logical tab order**: Follows visual layout
- ‚úÖ **Skip links**: Jump to main content

```html
<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Keyboard accessible custom button -->
<div 
  role="button" 
  tabindex="0"
  onclick="handleClick()">
  Custom Button
</div>

<script>
const customButton = document.querySelector('[role="button"][tabindex="0"]');
customButton.addEventListener('keydown', (event) => {
  // Trigger on Enter or Space
  if (event.key === 'Enter' || event.key === ' ') {
    event.preventDefault();
    handleClick();
  }
});
</script>

<style>
/* ‚úÖ Good: Clear focus indicator */
button:focus,
a:focus,
input:focus {
  outline: 3px solid #0066cc;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Alternative: custom focus ring */
*:focus-visible {
  outline: none;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.4);
}
</style>
```

#### Keyboard Shortcuts
- ‚úÖ **Standard shortcuts**: Tab, Shift+Tab, Enter, Space, Escape
- ‚úÖ **Arrow keys**: For lists, menus, sliders
- ‚úÖ **Home/End**: Jump to start/end
- ‚úÖ **Document shortcuts**: Avoid conflicting with browser

```javascript
// ‚úÖ Good: Keyboard navigation for custom dropdown
const dropdown = document.querySelector('[role="listbox"]');
const options = dropdown.querySelectorAll('[role="option"]');
let currentIndex = 0;

dropdown.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
  switch(e.key) {
    case 'ArrowDown':
      e.preventDefault();
      currentIndex = Math.min(currentIndex + 1, options.length - 1);
      options[currentIndex].focus();
      break;
      
    case 'ArrowUp':
      e.preventDefault();
      currentIndex = Math.max(currentIndex - 1, 0);
      options[currentIndex].focus();
      break;
      
    case 'Home':
      e.preventDefault();
      currentIndex = 0;
      options[0].focus();
      break;
      
    case 'End':
      e.preventDefault();
      currentIndex = options.length - 1;
      options[currentIndex].focus();
      break;
      
    case 'Enter':
    case ' ':
      e.preventDefault();
      options[currentIndex].click();
      break;
      
    case 'Escape':
      closeDropdown();
      break;
  }
});
```

### Images and Media

#### Alternative Text
- ‚úÖ **Descriptive alt text**: Describe image purpose/content
- ‚úÖ **Empty alt for decorative**: `alt=""`
- ‚úÖ **Don't use "image of"**: Screen readers announce it's an image
- ‚úÖ **Keep concise**: 125 characters or less

```html
<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Descriptive alt text -->
<img 
  src="chart.png" 
  alt="Bar chart showing sales increased 50% in Q4">

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Empty alt for decorative -->
<img src="decorative-pattern.png" alt="">

<!-- ‚úÖ Good: Complex image with longdesc -->
<img 
  src="complex-diagram.png" 
  alt="Network architecture diagram"
  aria-describedby="diagram-desc">
<div id="diagram-desc" class="sr-only">
  Detailed description: The diagram shows a three-tier architecture 
  with web servers, application servers, and database servers...
</div>

<!-- ‚ùå Bad: Generic or missing alt -->
<img src="photo.jpg" alt="image">
<img src="logo.png">  <!-- Missing alt -->
```

