### Color Contrast

#### WCAG Requirements
- ‚úÖ **Normal text**: 4.5:1 minimum (AA), 7:1 (AAA)
- ‚úÖ **Large text**: 3:1 minimum (AA), 4.5:1 (AAA)
- ‚úÖ **UI components**: 3:1 minimum
- ‚úÖ **Test all combinations**: Use contrast checkers

```css
/* ‚úÖ Good: Sufficient contrast */
:root {
  /* Text on white background */
  --text-primary: #111827;     /* 16.5:1 - AAA */
  --text-secondary: #4b5563;   /* 8.6:1 - AAA */
  --text-tertiary: #6b7280;    /* 5.7:1 - AA */
  
  /* Links */
  --link-color: #0066cc;       /* 7.7:1 - AAA */
  
  /* Buttons */
  --button-bg: #0066cc;
  --button-text: #ffffff;      /* 7.7:1 on blue */
  
  /* Success/Error */
  --success-text: #047857;     /* 6.4:1 - AAA */
  --error-text: #b91c1c;       /* 7.1:1 - AAA */
}

/* ‚ùå Bad: Insufficient contrast */
.low-contrast {
  color: #cccccc;              /* 1.6:1 - Fails WCAG */
  background: #ffffff;
}

/* ‚úÖ Good: Proper contrast */
.good-contrast {
  color: #666666;              /* 5.7:1 - Passes AA */
  background: #ffffff;
}
```

